about.summary: Pathlib Extension for AWS S3 Service, to provide File-System/Path like interface

name: s3path
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "s3path" %}
{% set version = "0.1.8" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 71a00b7714d0555d3588a46db20fcda9c1f1cb611232ee5563e89e291e3ae7a1

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - s3path

about:
  home: https://github.com/liormizr/s3path
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Pathlib Extension for AWS S3 Service, to provide File-System/Path like interface'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - liormizr
